Maps - Plot Universities across USA

The Domain

IPEDS is the primary source of information on U.S Colleges, Universities, technical and vaccational institutions. The purpose of this report is to explore map visualization with the American University data.

Dataset

Dataset has details about the universities and colleges in USA for year 2013. It has details of degrees’ offered,enrollment, graduation and fees and so on. Data set has university details along with their geo locations.

The dataset provided at https://public.tableau.com/en-us/s/resources. It is called “American University Data”. This is a smaller version of dataset available at https://nces.ed.gov/ipeds/Home/UseTheData.
